                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.00/1804</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-04-16T12:00:00-04:40">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 16, 1916, noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>President practically prisoner in his country place. Arias has placed censorship
                    on messages and telegrams of the President and committed other acts of open
                    rebellion. I am daily with the President and he is now determined not to resign
                    but if Arias persists will ask for his resignation or dismissal.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
